ActNavigable Waters Protection Act
SubjectProclamation Exempting the Waters of Lake Pignac and Lake B from the Operation of Section 22 of the Act
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION be issued declaring the WATERS OF LAKE PIGNAC AND LAKE B, located in Quebec, be exempt from the application of section 22 of the Navigable Waters Protection Act with respect to the depositing of waste rock piles by Cliffs Natural Resources Inc.
